The paper also mentions the use of genetic algorithms, neural networks, and sensor networks, which are commonly used in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the use of strategies employed by certain species, which could fall under the category of swarm intelligence (cs.SI). Finally, the paper discusses the need for new offensive and defensive techniques, which could fall under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
